---- ALGORITHMS ----
>> C2: Explain how you read and write to the console for the kernel monitor.
use input_getc() to get input from keyboard;
if it reads a 'return', it will read the command;
if it is "whoami", it will write my name to the console;
if it is "exit", it will stop interacting;
if it is something else. it will write "invalid command" to the console;


